text: Paula Ruiz (born 16 February 1999) is a Spanish swimmer, specialising in open water events. She competed in the women's 10 km event at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, finishing in 24th place. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female long-distance swimmers
